[Analysis of characteristics and therapy of clients in the extension methadone 
maintenance therapy clinic].

[Article in Chinese]

Zhang G(1), Yang Y, Tang R, Hu Y, Xue H, Shan D, Feng Y, Duan S, Sun J(2).

