The clinical role and cost-effectiveness of long-acting antiretroviral therapy.

Ross EL(1), Weinstein MC(2), Schackman BR(3), Sax PE(4), Paltiel AD(5), Walensky 
RP(6), Freedberg KA(7), Losina E(8).

Author information:
(1)Division of General Internal Medicine Division of Medical Practice Evaluation 
